DOCKERIZED OPENJDK

  Dockerized java and javac executables using OpenJDK 8.

BUILD IMAGE

  make

  or

  make build

INSTALL EXECUTABLES

  make install

  or

  make install_java
  make install_javac

USAGE

  First, add these lines to your .bashrc to ensure ~/bin is in your PATH:

    if ! echo "${PATH}" | grep -Eq "(^|:)${HOME}/bin(:|$)"; then
      export PATH=${HOME}/bin:${PATH}
    fi

  Then...

    javac ClassName.java
    java ClassName

UNINSTALL EXECUTABLES

  make uninstall

  or

  make uninstall_java
  make uninstall_javac
